videos.description: Georgetown's Mac McClung drives to the basket and adjusts his shot in midair for the layup.
videos.headline: McClung adjusts for nifty layup

videos.description: Syracuse's Tyus Battle attacks the basket for a pair of tough buckets to start the second half.
videos.headline: Battle single-handedly starts Cuse rally
